al\ncontrol setup is verified to be the most effective in reducing the pressure\nroot-mean-square level up to 52% along the aft and bottom cavity walls compared\nto the baseline cavity flow. The present flow control guideline derived from\nresolvent analysis should be applicable to flows that require the actuation\ninput to remain effective over an extended region of interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2020 06:07:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
