 phases. We also present results of a theoretical study of a\nrealistic model which, in addition to replicating our experimental results,\nexplains the origin of the topological insulating bulk and helical edge-modes.\nOur experimental and theoretical results establish a viable route to realizing\nthe time-reversal invariant $\\mathbb{Z}_2$ topological phase of matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2020 14:22:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2020 07:04:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-01"}
